summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Latona Avenue from East Forty-fifth Street to East Forty-second Street in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 15112, creating Local Improvement District No. 1382 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
